00:19:44,875 --> 00:19:46,416
[LUNAR PAPA] Human.

484
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:50,250
You can either take
responsibility, or die.

485
00:19:50,625 --> 00:19:53,250
[LUNAR PAPA] Responsibility.
Responsibility.

486
00:19:53,916 --> 00:19:56,833
You'll marry Lunar or die.

487
00:19:56,916 --> 00:19:58,375
What? Marry Lunar?

488
00:19:58,833 --> 00:20:01,916
--[DAD] Already? At his age?
--[MOM] No. Engaged twice?

489
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,916
Yeah, good for
you, Naughty-sumi!

490
00:20:04,916 --> 00:20:06,583
Really, Lunar?

491
00:20:06,666 --> 00:20:09,166
Well, Sun. Yeah.
Th-That's right!

492
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:12,541
Nagasumi has to learn to take
responsibility for his actions.

493
00:20:12,625 --> 00:20:15,291
[Lunar fake laughs]

494
00:20:17,625 --> 00:20:20,541
I'll go ahead and take
your son with me right now.

495
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:22,208
Mr. and Mrs. Michishio,

496
00:20:22,291 --> 00:20:23,541
I'll send someone
to get you when

497
00:20:23,625 --> 00:20:25,875
we're ready to perform
the ceremony. Got it?

498
00:20:25,958 --> 00:20:27,375
[MOM AND DAD] Uh yes!

499
00:20:27,458 --> 00:20:28,916
Hold on, Edomae!

500
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,875
I've got somethin' that
I need to say to ya!

501
00:20:32,500 --> 00:20:33,916
Good job!

502
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:34,916
Nagasumi!

503
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,916
No, Sun, stop it.
Let Nagasumi go.

504
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:38,750
Here, drink this.

505
00:20:38,833 --> 00:20:40,000
Hey, thanks!

506
00:20:40,083 --> 00:20:40,875
--[both laugh]
--[NAGASUMI] You're so tense.

507
00:20:40,958 --> 00:20:42,208
[GOZABURO] You're good at that!

508
00:20:42,291 --> 00:20:44,041
I'm afraid Nagasumi
isn't with us anymore!

509
00:20:44,125 --> 00:20:45,666
I'm right here?

510
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:46,833
Nagasumi, come back!

511
00:20:46,916 --> 00:20:48,416
I'm sorry!

512
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:50,416
Get goin' already,
you maggot.

513
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,875
[LUNAR] We're going.

514
00:20:54,791 --> 00:20:58,416
Nagasumi!

515
00:21:00,208 --> 00:21:02,083
[SARU] La la la la!

516
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,916
[SARU] Hey, a helicopter.
My lord, look.

517
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,958
There's a helicopter over there.

518
00:21:08,041 --> 00:21:09,583
[KAI] Whoa look at 'er go!

519
00:21:09,666 --> 00:21:11,375
[KAI AND SARU] Hey!

520
00:21:11,458 --> 00:21:14,583
[NAGASUMI] Chimp! Mikawa!
Hurry you guys, help!

521
00:21:14,666 --> 00:21:17,958
Woo-hoo! We got to see a
helicopter today. How cool!

522
00:21:18,041 --> 00:21:20,583
[NAGASUMI] Morons!

523
00:21:25,916 --> 00:21:28,958
I think that this is probably
all for the best, Miss Sun.

524
00:21:29,041 --> 00:21:30,875
Once you go back
to the Seto Sea,

525
00:21:30,958 --> 00:21:32,583
you'll forget about
him in no time.

526
00:21:32,666 --> 00:21:34,166
I won't though.

527
00:21:35,125 --> 00:21:37,708
[SUN] I can't help but feel
like part of this is my fault.

528
00:21:37,791 --> 00:21:38,958
Ya see, maybe
if I'd been a better

529
00:21:39,041 --> 00:21:40,916
bride ta be, this wouldn't
have happened.

530
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:43,666
But what can I do about it now?

531
00:21:44,083 --> 00:21:48,083
[SUN] Huh, Maki? What do I do?

532
00:21:49,125 --> 00:21:50,583
[Nagasumi cries out]

533
00:21:53,833 --> 00:21:55,083
Please, Lunar...

534
00:21:55,166 --> 00:21:59,041
Damn it. This is all a
misunderstanding, Sun!

535
00:22:00,041 --> 00:22:02,875
[NAGASUMI] Help, Sun!

536
00:22:04,291 --> 00:22:09,250
♪

537
00:23:34,666 --> 00:23:35,625
[NAGASUMI]
I've sure got a lot of life

538
00:23:35,708 --> 00:23:37,166
experience for someone my age!

539
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:39,333
I'm engaged for the
second time against my will.

540
00:23:39,416 --> 00:23:40,583
No, I'm telling you...

541
00:23:40,666 --> 00:23:42,041
Sun is my true bride!

542
00:23:42,125 --> 00:23:43,333
But now an all-out brawl between

543
00:23:43,416 --> 00:23:45,041
the yakuza families
is unavoidable.

544
00:23:45,125 --> 00:23:47,250
I must sacrifice my
life to accomplish...

545
00:23:47,333 --> 00:23:48,875
What would that
accomplish, exactly?

